text: Walter Probst (17 April 1918 – February 2007) was an Austrian football player and manager. ==Career== He played for Rapid Wien, Wacker München, Austria Wien, Hakoah and Sportclub. ==Manager== He coached IFK Göteborg, Austria Wien, Djurgårdens IF, Örgryte IS and Saab Linköping. ==Other websites== Rapid Wien Archiv:Players profile Category:1918 births Category:2007 deaths Category:Austrian footballers Category:Austrian football managers Category:Association football forwards Category:FK Austria Wien players Category:Austrian football forwards Category:Austrian football champions Category:SK Rapid Wien players
